---
export const prerender = true;

import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Nav from "../components/Nav.astro";
import Shell from "../layouts/Shell.astro";
---

<Shell>
	<Fragment slot="head">
		<title>
			craftlions | Modern Freelance IT Services, Technical Advisory & Product
			Development
		</title>
		<meta
			name="description"
			content="craftlions delivers focused IT services, technical advisory, workshops, and software development for teams that value clear communication and durable engineering."
		>
		<meta
			name="keywords"
			content="IT services, technical advisory, freelance developer, software consultant, modern web development, pair programming, workshops, asynchronous collaboration, future-proof technology, external technical expertise, software architecture, digital product development"
		>
		<meta
			property="og:title"
			content="Craftlions | Modern IT Services & Technical Advisory"
		>
		<meta
			property="og:description"
			content="Focused IT services and technical expertise for teams that value clarity, maintainability, and long-term software decisions."
		>
		<meta property="og:type" content="website">
	</Fragment>
	<Fragment slot="body">
		<body
			class="min-h-dvh grid grid-rows-[auto_1fr_auto] bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-950 dark:text-neutral-50 text-neutral-950 antialiased gap-12 p-4 text-pretty"
		>
			<header class="grid gap-6 justify-items-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<Nav deferSessionLinks variant="marketing" />
				<section class="grid gap-4">
					<h1
						class="border-l border-dashed border-neutral-400 pl-3 text-3xl font-semibold leading-tight dark:border-neutral-600"
					>
						Modern IT services drawn with care
					</h1>
					<p class="pl-3 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
						craftlions helps teams plan, build, and maintain software with a
						practical engineering mindset. The work is modern, but the process
						stays legible: clear lines, useful decisions, and outcomes that can
						be explained without decoration.
					</p>
					<p class="pl-3 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
						From product development and technical strategy to workshops and
						hands-on delivery, craftlions brings focused external expertise into
						your existing process. The standard is simple:
						<strong>
							build carefully, communicate plainly, and leave systems easier to
							trust.
						</strong>
					</p>
				</section>
				<section class="justify-self-start pl-3">
					<Button href="mailto:alexander@craftlions.com">
						Start a project
					</Button>
				</section>
			</header>

			<main class="w-full grid content-start min-h-0 max-w-3xl mx-auto gap-12">
				<section class="grid gap-6">
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
						Services for steady technical progress
					</h2>
					<article
						class="grid gap-3 border-l border-dashed border-neutral-300 pl-3 dark:border-neutral-700"
					>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Software development</h3>
						<p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
							craftlions builds with modern technologies when they serve the
							product, not because they are fashionable. The goal is software
							that is scalable, maintainable, and still understandable after the
							first release.
						</p>
					</article>
					<article
						class="grid gap-3 border-l border-dashed border-neutral-300 pl-3 dark:border-neutral-700"
					>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Flexible and asynchronous</h3>
						<p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
							Work can move without filling the calendar. craftlions supports
							async-first collaboration, clear written updates, and real-time
							conversation when it helps unblock decisions.
						</p>
					</article>
					<article
						class="grid gap-3 border-l border-dashed border-neutral-300 pl-3 dark:border-neutral-700"
					>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">
							Technical advisory and strategy
						</h3>
						<p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
							Strong products need decisions that survive contact with real
							constraints. craftlions helps evaluate options, define
							implementation paths, and reduce risk before complexity becomes
							expensive.
						</p>
					</article>
					<article
						class="grid gap-3 border-l border-dashed border-neutral-300 pl-3 dark:border-neutral-700"
					>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Workshops and learning</h3>
						<p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
							Workshops are shaped around the team and the work in front of it:
							architecture choices, implementation patterns, delivery process,
							or practical skills that make better decisions easier.
						</p>
					</article>
					<section>
						<Button href="mailto:alexander@craftlions.com">
							Discuss the work
						</Button>
					</section>
				</section>
				<section
					class="grid gap-6 border-t border-dashed border-neutral-300 pt-6 dark:border-neutral-700"
				>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Why choose craftlions?</h2>
					<p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
						Quality is not a finish-line activity. It starts with choosing the
						right scope, naming tradeoffs clearly, and balancing
						maintainability, performance, and business value from the beginning.
					</p>
					<ul
						class="grid gap-2 pl-5 text-neutral-700 list-disc marker:text-neutral-400 dark:text-neutral-300 dark:marker:text-neutral-600"
					>
						<li>Experience with modern technology across multiple sectors.</li>
						<li>Reliable delivery with practical technical depth.</li>
						<li
							>Solutions shaped around business goals and operating reality.</li
						>
						<li>Clear integration with your processes, tools, and cadence.</li>
						<li
							>Work accepted only when it can be delivered to a high standard.</li
						>
					</ul>
				</section>
				<section
					class="grid gap-6 border-t border-dashed border-neutral-300 pt-6 dark:border-neutral-700"
				>
					<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">
						Let's build something better together
					</h2>
					<p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
						craftlions helps businesses build smarter with modern IT services,
						technical advisory, and hands-on product development support.
						Whether you need a reliable technology partner, software
						architecture expertise, or strategic technical guidance, we create
						practical, scalable solutions built for long-term success.
					</p>
					<p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
						The work goes beyond writing code. It strengthens the technical
						foundation, reduces unnecessary complexity, and keeps architecture
						aligned with the business it supports.
					</p>
					<p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300">
						If you are looking for a technical partner that brings external
						expertise, strategic clarity, creative problem-solving, and a
						commitment to careful delivery, craftlions is ready to help.
					</p>
					<section>
						<Button href="mailto:alexander@craftlions.com">
							Get in touch
						</Button>
					</section>
				</section>
			</main>
			<Footer />
		</body>
	</Fragment>
</Shell>
